      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DESTINY LANE (1) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only half a length (35.30) behind Canya Celeste at Cannington. Can find winning form. WHISKEY GRACE (2) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at five of nine starts including two wins but missed the frame latest when fifth (36.27) over 622m at Richmond. Strike rate this course strong having won two of three tries. Has the ability and rates a key chance this line-up. PAW YARRA (8) was a last start winner (25.99) at this track who is building a strong winning record. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. PELOPONNESE (5) racing over this distance brings the best out in her.",
